        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "屋漏更遭连夜雨，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "行船偏遇打头风。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉钟元甫。所生一儿，名叫子期。只因去岁在马鞍山前砍樵，偶遇晋国大夫"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俞伯牙。他二人共谈琴律，情投意合，结为金兰之好。临别之时，又赠吾儿黄"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金二笏。约定今秋还在马鞍山前相会。我儿回得家来，白日砍柴，夜晚攻书，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "朝思暮想，偶得病症而亡。今乃百日之期，老汉备得纸钱，去到坟前烧化，以"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "表父子之情。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家有万贯终何用，老来无子落场空。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老眼昏花路难寻，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳听得树林内百鸟喧声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "羊羔也有跪乳情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "白发人反送儿黑发身。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟元甫下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "二黄",
        "musical_styles": [
          "二黄原板"
        ]
      },
      "scene_feature": [
        1.0,
