    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "他的父即我父双膝跪倒",
        "俞伯牙",
        "我儿常说俞伯牙",
        "樵夫",
        "渔夫",
        "童儿",
        "钟元甫"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙、童儿同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "昨晚间抚瑶琴内藏悲调，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "抚不着钟子期所为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "但不知集贤村路走哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，来此双阳岔道，但不知哪条道路，可通集贤村？那旁有一老丈，等他到"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，问个明白。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟元甫上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "断香烟绝后代此罪非小，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可叹我年迈人无有下梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官请了！敢是迷失路径？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问的何处？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请问老丈，此地可有一集贤村么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官你来看，东十里也是集贤村，西十里也是集贤村，但未知问的哪个集贤村？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老丈你且少待。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎吓，贤弟，既有两个集贤村，为何不对愚兄说明，叫我哪里去问？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官背地沉吟，敢是指路不明？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉居住有数年，无有不是亲朋。但不知问的哪一家？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "拜访钟子期贤弟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你待怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "钟子期！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说提起子期话，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由老汉泪如麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不知是他不是他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官你来迟了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿常说俞伯牙"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么来迟了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官有所不知：老汉钟元甫，亡儿子期，只因去岁在马鞍山前砍樵，偶遇着晋"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国大夫俞什么……"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是俞伯牙？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不错，俞伯牙！他二人共谈琴律，彼此相投，结为金兰之好；临行之时，赠他"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄金二笏，约定今秋还在马鞍山前相会。我儿回到家来，白日砍樵，夜晚读书，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "心思过度，偶得病症而亡了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才怎讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一命亡了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！哎贤弟吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，此位何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "童儿",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是晋国上大夫俞大人便是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是钟贤弟把命丧了，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙晕。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀大人醒来，大人醒来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙醒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我腹内好一似万把钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他的父即我父双膝跪倒"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "问答人施一礼所为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我就是俞伯牙伯父不晓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "贤弟死留何言细说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的儿临死前亦曾言道："
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "埋至在马鞍山候驾来瞧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "既如此老伯父向前引道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这就是新坟台不孝儿曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "见坟台不由人双膝跪倒，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我心中好一似走马断桥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哭一声钟贤弟何方去了？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可怜我万水千山空走一遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓伯父，侄儿在此一祭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉代谢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓，俞大人前来祭奠与你吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "童儿，将瑶琴摆在坟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（童儿允，摆琴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此空枉费，人情赴东流。只因渺茫去，存留土一丘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄慢三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想去岁在山前论琴交好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄慢三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "曾结拜如同那一母同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "分别时约定了今秋来到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "因此上辞王驾来走一遭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "兄为你不愿穿平带蟒袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "钟贤弟在阴曹你可知晓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有几代古圣贤细听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "齐景公哭吴婴君臣相交；"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "羊角哀亦哭过左伯桃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "俞伯牙哭子期皆因是，想去岁闲游在马鞍山道，谈谈讲讲，论论琴调。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄快三眼",
          "musical_style": "二黄快三眼",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哭一声钟贤弟何方去了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔夫、樵夫同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "六月炉边炼铁，数九江上渔翁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "樵夫",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "非是不知寒暑，生涯落在其中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫、樵夫",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了请了，你我无事，看此人讲些什么。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙抚琴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "渔夫、樵夫",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看此人对着坟前，不知弄什么。你我好笑吓，哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（渔夫、樵夫同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯父，他二人为何发笑而去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他二人不晓琴律，故而发笑而去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是二渔樵琴律不晓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由我俞伯牙心似火烧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙摔琴。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "问大人摔此琴所为哪条？"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "摔碎瑶琴凤尾寒，子期不再对谁弹。春风满面皆朋友，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "三叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！贤弟吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要想知音难上难了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "问伯父贤弟死家有何靠？"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "祖居在集贤村家业萧条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫童儿取黄金伯父养老，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "与贤弟春秋祭买纸烧化。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀大人，慢说小老儿，就是亡儿子期，亦感恩非浅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "辞伯父，别子期，扬长就道，"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可叹他年迈人无有下梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓伯父，侄到家去，差人迎接伯父伯母，那时不要推辞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "相逢不久分别早，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他二人结拜如同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "伯牙在，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "子期死呀……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙、钟元甫同哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "再与伯父说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伯父，侄儿走后，不要想他了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾不想他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子期是我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是子期。告辞了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "俞伯牙",
          "line_type": "叫头",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟！子期！哎呀贤弟吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（俞伯牙下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "送大人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "子期儿吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "似这等金兰友世间少有，"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "回家去与妈妈细说根苗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "钟元甫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿吓……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（钟元甫下。）"
        }
      ],
